[[File:Retniw.png|thumb|right|280px]]
'''Retniw''' was an [[elder rune]] indicating a place for camping.

Found throughout the [[Sea of Fallen Stars]] region, this rune was a variant of [[Lammath]] but designated a pre-existing campsite or a building that could offer shelter.
